<title>USA: Kuhlman sets public offering price.</title>
<headline>Kuhlman sets public offering price.</headline>
<dateline>ATLANTA 1997-06-24</dateline>
<text>
<p>Kuhlman Corp said it has set a public offering of up to 2.5 million common shares at $28-7/8 per share.</p>
<p>All of the shares are being sold by the company. The net proceeds, which could reach as much as $68 million, are to be used primarily to reduce outstanding debt that has been incurred to fund the company's previous growth and acquisition activities.</p>
<p>In addition, Kuhlman said it is using a portion of the proceeds to redeem outstanding warrants to purchase 480,750 shares of common stock held by a former lender. -- New York Newsdesk 212-859-1610</p>
